node.text:
Set amongst the dramatic landscape of Barbados’ East Coast, Zazen is a totally unique, ultra-modern escape like no other. Cutting-edge architecture is boldly brought to life in polished concrete and agate amidst a tropical breeze and the sound of waves crashing in the distance.
On making your grand entrance, discover the very finest luxury interiors set in an awe-inspiring 6,000 sq. ft. of pure luxury. Open-plan living spills out over the infinity pool, across the white sand and above and beyond the magnificent Atlantic Ocean – and the finest surf the island has to offer. For anything else, our bespoke concierge service will ensure every other detail is just as perfect.
Check @diamantemglobalportfolio for more details.
#diamantemglobalportfolio #designers_need

node.text:
The extra long bed frame and the ingeniously positioned headboard of the seemingly floating dream site. Thanks to its inclined position it is very comfortable if you want to read or watch TV in bed. But at the same time an additional surface is created behind the headboard which serves as a useful shelf for important things such as books, reading glasses and snuggle blanket. Available in natural treated solid wood: ash, beech, core beech, cherry, maple, oak, knotty oak, walnut, knotty walnut. In the SOMNIA bed – as in all other beds from vitamin design – health, design and material make a successful connection.
Tap here for more: ➡ https://www.modumshop.com/products/bed-somnia .....
.
